Sentence: We are going to start the project Monday.
We : pronoun, first person plural, subject of the verb «are going»
are : auxiliary verb, part of the «be going to» future construction
going : main verb, present participle, part of the «be going to» future construction
to : preposition, introduces the infinitive verb «start»
